----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Third-party components and attributions
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

This plugin is a third-party extension for Jellyfin (https://jellyfin.org/)
and is not affiliated with or endorsed by the Jellyfin project. Jellyfin
itself is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2.0.

The plugin references the following NuGet packages at build time, which
remain the property of their respective authors and retain their own
licenses:

  - Jellyfin.Controller            (GPL-2.0)  https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin
  - Jellyfin.Model                 (GPL-2.0)  https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin
  - Jellyfin.Database.Implementations (GPL-2.0)  https://github.com/jellyfin/jellyfin

Optional integration with the FileTransformation plugin by IAmParadox27
(https://github.com/IAmParadox27/jellyfin-plugin-file-transformation) for
client-side script injection that enables preroll support before TV episodes.
The plugin auto-detects FileTransformation at runtime and degrades gracefully
when it isn't installed (movies still work).

The bundled web client patch (`playback-hook.js`) is original work distributed
under the same MIT license as the rest of the plugin. It interacts only with
Jellyfin's public `playbackManager` and `ApiClient` JavaScript APIs.

